name: Insense Time! Runner Up
description:
Controls

Pressing the up key will let you jump. You don't need to use the right or left keys because Red Dog runs by himself. You just need to time your jumps right. The Boss in the game, Evil Cat is hard to beat. All the tips I have is that if Evil cat blocks your way, you can walk through stairs and pass right by. If you die, press the gray flag to restart.
